race.description: Rmbl Investments Rising Stars Race Handicap
race.comment: SAVAMOON (7) ran a solid race first up at Kilmore when beaten just over a length into third in a BM66, doing enough there to suggest he'd come back well. His form last time in progressed nicely and he'll strip fitter for this. YAM (1) is racing okay without winning. The past couple have been good, and this is slightly easier than last time through the same race as SAVAMOON. FROZEN TIDE (6) was okay at this level last time out at Donald when getting back in a race that turned into a dash home. The win prior in easier company was solid and he might settle closer from the inside gate. LUVYA MUMMA (9) resumes. She got over far more ground in some handy races last time in but this trip should be okay first up and she has the class to figure.
